Media Coverage Tracker (News Classification)  

Scrape daily news articles about coal, energy, or CCL, and classify them as “Positive PR”, “Negative PR”, or “Neutral”. Why useful: PR can track their brand’s media coverage daily. Beginner-friendly tools: Python + Scikit-learn (Naive Bayes classifier). 

 

Steps: 

Created a dummy dataset 

Vectorize text 

Detect Patterns using Naïve Bayes Classifier 

Train using Training data 

Test on new articles 

Tried enhancing using SVM. 
